Ukraine
. We are sincerely thankful to J. Divay (Royal Tyrrell Museum of Palaeontology, Drumheller, 
Canada
), N. Dykan (Institute of Geological Sciences, National Academy of Sciences of 
Ukraine
), T. Grande (Loyola University Chicago, 
USA
), and N. Trif (Brukenthal National Museum, 
Romania
) for their useful comments and advice. We also wish to thank T. Přikryl (Institute of Geology of the Czech Academy of Sciences) for consultations, and Z. Barkaszi (National Museum of Natural History, National Academy of Sciences of 
Ukraine
) for proofreading the manuscript.
